1. Project Idea & Objective

We started with the idea of building a low-cost autonomous surveillance rover that can:

Move through an unknown indoor environment

Detect obstacles

Create a digital map using LiDAR

Estimate its position (localization)

Be useful for defence surveillance and reconnaissance

2.COMPONENTS REQUIRED:
Raspberry pi 5 4gb
L298N motor driver
BO motors (4)
Ultrasonic sensor
jumper wires
wheels and chassis
12v battery
power bank(for Raspberry pi)

